Introduction

Geumhee is a South Korean rapper, dancer and singer under A2Z Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group CSR.

In December 2023, Geumhee was revealed to be a contestant on WeTV's survival show "Chuang Asia" alongside fellow CSR members Duna, Seoyeon and Yeham.
